SEND TO A FRIEND






                                                                                Booz Allen Hamilton Holding Corporation is (Booz Allen or “the company”) is one of the leading providers of management consulting, technology and engineering services to the US government in defense, intelligence, and civil markets, and to major corporations and not-for-profit organizations. The company primarily operates in the US where it is headquartered in McLean, Virginia and employed 22,700 people as of March 31, 2014.
                                                                            

